Author: newsilike
Title: [ANN][ICO] CBNT is a decentralized professional content sharing community
Body: WHITEPAPER | WEBSITE | TWITTER | TELEGRAM | FACEBOOK | MEDIUM | STEEMIT | BOUNTY    CBNT is a decentralized professional content sharing community based on blockchain technology and an ecosystem model of DPGC (Decentralization Professional Generated Content). In the beginning, we will focus on blockchain and professional financial investment content. CBNT will create a win-win ecosystem for all participants, including content/articles providers, content readers (viewer), ad publishers, and token holders. In the CBNT community, whether you are content generators or content viewers, both sides can receive tokens “Mining Rewards”. As CBNT grows and traffic boosts, all the profit of numerous ads will also be distributed to all of the participants.    -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  Bounty Campaign -- Coming Soon  AirDrop Campaign -- Coming Soon  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
